msgid ""
"Some of the variables you have entered for analysis are not binary or "
"ordinal. Please make sure that all variables are binary or ordinal or change "
"the model to gcgm."
msgstr ""
"Algunhas das variables que introduciches para a análise non son binarias nin "
"ordinais. Por favor, asegúrate de que todas as variables son binarias ou "
"ordinais, ou troca o modelo a GCGM."

msgid ""
"Minimum edge strength ignored in the network plot because it was larger than "
